{"tid":2461842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布林肯：美歐現時合作 比近年任何時候都重要  共同應對中國","createTime":"2021-03-25T15:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T15:20:00.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc99cbe938ee968a11373d8e8c5eb54e42c26492","tid":2461842,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"布林肯稱美歐現時合作比近年任何時候都重要<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿布林肯表示，美國與盟友之間現時的合作，比近年任何時候都重要，強調美國與北約及歐盟的關係，對克服挑戰至關重要。在布魯塞爾訪問的最後一日，布林肯與比利時外長維爾梅斯會面。布林肯表示，今次行程焦點是要表明美國決心振興美歐之間的聯盟及夥伴關係，指出拜登政府的基本宗旨，是盡早及經常諮詢美國的盟友，華府有信心透過這種長遠關係，與歐盟及北約克服各種挑戰。他又承諾，在全球分配安全及有效的新冠疫苗問題上，與歐盟及北約合作，確保他們能為將來的疫情大流行做好準備。今次是布林肯出任國務卿後首次出訪歐洲，他較早前與歐盟達成共識，重啟關於中國議題的雙邊對話機制，合作應對中國的挑戰行為。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-25 23:00:20<br />\n<br />\nhttps://<del><a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582634-20210325.htm?spTabChangea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582634-20210325.htm%3FspTabChangea&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=65d3cbcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582634-20210325.htm%3FspTabChangea&h=5609eb1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582634-20210325.htm?spTabChangea</a></del>ble=0"},{"pid":"dfe97ace382b3ea22cc9a67abb65779a0eb8c354","tid":2461842,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"仲應咩對,聯軍出兵滅支那好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9651dac689bd9f4457563af9116d85ffa8cb4418","tid":2461842,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUQT3ek3v2BKL6gad8Gxg5FMdv8AVscu1oCJ3b1adVaj2?filename=vQCMoMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQCMoMx.jpg&h=b9aaa2bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ecae8d26b638c0c7e77593217dea2e2eec